title: Tim Timinee Tim Timinee Tim Tim to You (Video 2016)
overview: Watch as he emerges from a chimney to take the roof off! ‘Tim Timinee Tim Timinee Tim Tim to you’ is the latest lorry load of nonsense from the one-liner pelting, silly singing, prop flinging comedian.
storyline: 'Tim Timinee Tim Timinee Tim Tim to you' is the latest lorry load of nonsense from the one-liner pelting, silly singing, prop flinging comedian. The sell-out show that Tim took around the country and beyond is now heading for your living room. Take a deep breath everyone, because there's a lot to get through. Standby for a large number of stupid jokes, (and platypuses on poles).
